In a saucepan, bring cream to a boil over medium heat. Remove from heat. Add chocolate and bourbon and whisk until melted and smooth. Let cool for 5 minutes before serving. Store in a glass jar in the refrigerator. Reheat in the microwave as needed. Let sauce thicken for 5 minutes before using. Variation Omit the bourbon for a G rating and add 2 tsp (10 mL) vanilla extract.